Package: docker-ipv6-firewall
Version: 1.2.0
Section: net
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: python3 (>= 3.9), python3-docker, python3-yaml, iptables, systemd
Maintainer: Sam <sam@example.com>
Description: Docker IPv6 Firewall Manager
 Automatically manages IPv6 firewall rules for Docker containers.
 .
 This service monitors Docker container events and automatically
 creates/removes IPv6 firewall rules based on container port
 exposures and network configurations.
 .
 Features:
  - Automatic Docker container monitoring
  - Dynamic IPv6 firewall rule management
  - Macvlan network support
  - Systemd service integration
  - Duplicate rule prevention
